rveillance and identified our assets. \{bureau_name\} favor failed.","\{surveillance_target\} departed the area before surveillance could be established. Product undeliverable. \{bureau_name\} disappointed.","Technical surveillance failed \'97 target used methods that defeated our capability. \{bureau_name\} product incomplete. Favor not fulfilled.","Surveillance aborted when local law enforcement became involved. \{surveillance_target\} alerted. \{bureau_name\} favor compromised.","Team compromised mid-operation. Partial product only delivered to \{bureau_name\}. Favor considered incomplete. Relationship impact negative."],"confSuccess":[4,8],"confFail":[-5,-10],"intelFields":[\{"key":"target_profile_field","label":"TARGET PROFILE","value":"BELLHOP \'97 profile partially confirmed","revealed":false\},\{"key":"bureau_case_field","label":"BUREAU CASE CONTEXT","value":"a foreign intelligence officer rolled-up case follow-on \'97 case context confirmed by BUREAU liaison","revealed":false\},\{"key":"surveillance_status","label":"SURVEILLANCE STATUS","value":"Surveillance initiated \'97 coverage not yet complete","revealed":false\},\{"key":"product_quality","label":"INTELLIGENCE PRODUCT","value":"Partial product \'97 some gaps in coverage remain","revealed":false\}],"intelBonus":false,"blown":false,"blownDaysLeft":0,"lastInvOutcome":null,"agencyJustification":"BUREAU has flagged a subject under an ongoing counter-espionage case. Their legal window is closed \'97 they need eyes-on through an alternate channel. SAA covert surveillance authority provides the access BUREAU cannot legally obtain. Successful completion of this favor will strengthen the inter-agency relationship.","favorOf":"BUREAU","favorAgencyName":"The Bureau (FBI)"\},\{"id":"M128","typeId":"SURVEILLANCE_TAKEDOWN","codename":"ZIRCON ESTUARY","threat":2,"label":"SURVEILLANCE CHAIN","category":"SURVEILLANCE / TAKEDOWN","location":"DOMESTIC","city":"Washington D.C.","country":"United States","urgency":45,"urgen