["Surveillance package established without compromise","Surveillance initiated \'97 pattern of life not yet established"]\},"opNarrative":"A discreet surveillance package is established on \{suspect_name\}. Field teams conduct rolling surveillance on foot and vehicle. SIGINT passively monitors digital footprint. The goal is to map the subject's daily routine, identify associates, and locate any operational infrastructure \'97 without alerting the subject.","investigateReports":["Subject \{suspect_name\} has been flagged as \{target_type\}. Initial surveillance authorization requested. Current location: \{city\}.","Intelligence flagged \{suspect_name\} as potentially \{target_type\}. Profile matches known patterns. Surveillance recommended before action.","Tip received: \{suspect_name\} may be \{target_type\}. Location: \{city\}. Surveillance package requested.","Counter-intelligence review flagged \{suspect_name\}. Assessed as \{target_type\}. Recommend immediate surveillance."],"fullBriefs":["SURVEILLANCE ASSESSMENT \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 1\\n\\nSubject \{suspect_name\}: \{suspect_profile\}. Surveillance established.\\n\\nInitial pattern-of-life shows: \{pattern_detail\}. Contact identified: \{contact_role\} meeting \{contact_frequency\}.\\n\\nRecommendation: Extend surveillance and conduct evidence collection at subject's premises.","SURVEILLANCE ASSESSMENT \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 1\\n\\nSubject \{suspect_name\} under active surveillance in \{city\}.\\n\\n\{pattern_detail\}. Three unidentified associates have been observed. Digital footprint shows \{digital_anomaly\}.\\n\\nRecommend proceeding to Phase 2: Evidence Collection.","SURVEILLANCE ASSESSMENT \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 1\\n\\n\{suspect_name\}: \{suspect_profile\}. Surveillance complete.\\n\\nPattern of life mapped. Contact: \{contact_role\}, meeting \{contact_frequency\}. Digital: \{digital_anomaly\}.\\n\\nEvidence collection phase recommended."],"successOutcomes":["Surveillance phase complete. \{suspect_name\}'s full routine mapped. \{contact_role\} confirmed as regular contact. Proceeding to evidence collection phase.","Phase 1 complete. Surveillance package maintained without compromise. \{digital_anomaly\} flagged for analysis. Phase 2 authorized.","Surveillance successful. Pattern of life established for \{suspect_name\}. Contact activity and digital anomalies documented. Phase 2 ready.","\{suspect_name\} under full surveillance. Routine mapped, associates identified. Proceeding to evidence collection."],"failureOutcomes":["Surveillance detected. Subject \{suspect_name\} has gone to ground. Operation will need to be rebuilt from scratch.","Surveillance package blown \'97 a counter-surveillance team spotted our assets. \{suspect_name\} has changed behavior.","\{suspect_name\} performed a surveillance detection route and identified our team. Subject has gone dark.","Technical surveillance compromised. \{suspect_name\} switched devices and changed patterns. Phase 1 inconclusive."]\},\{"id":"EVIDENCE_SEARCH","name":"Phase 2: Evidence Collection","shortName":"EVIDENCE","invDaysRange":[2,4],"invDepts":["FIELD_OPS","COUNTER_INTEL","ANALYSIS"],"execDaysRange":[1,2],"execDepts":["FIELD_OPS"],"budgetRange":[2,4],"confSuccess":[0,0],"confFail":[-5,-10],"falseFlagChance":0.3,"invDeptEfficiency":\{"FIELD_OPS":80,"COUNTER_INTEL":85,"ANALYSIS":70\},"intelFields":[\{"key":"premises_status","label":"PREMISES STATUS"\},\{"key":"entry_window","label":"ENTRY WINDOW"\},\{"key":"evidence_targets","label":"EVIDENCE TARGETS"\}],"intelFieldValues":\{"premises_status":["\{premises_type\} of \{suspect_name\} identified and fully cased","\{premises_type\} identified \'97 casing incomplete, entry risk uncharacterized"],"entry_window":["\{entry_window\} \'97 confirmed, subject movement tracked","Entry window estimated \'97 subject schedule partially established"],"evidence_targets":["\{search_focus\} \'97 specific targets identified by analysis","Evidence targets preliminary \'97 subject profile requires more work"]\},"falseFlagTexts":["ANOMALY DETECTED \'97 \{suspect_name\}'s premises yielded unexpected findings. The \\"suspicious\\" communications are personal in nature. Financial records show legitimate sources. The subject appears to be an unwitting associate of the actual target, not a principal actor.","INVESTIGATION UPDATE \'97 Evidence is inconsistent with the threat profile. \{suspect_name\}'s contact with \{contact_role\} appears to be professional, not operational. Subject may have been used as an unwitting cut-out. Significant probability we have the wrong person."],"opNarrative":"Field Operations conducts a covert entry of the subject's residence and office premises while the subject is away, confirmed by the surveillance team. Counter-Intelligence analysts review collected materials on-site. SIGINT provides overwatch. The team is looking for operational documents, devices, foreign currency, or coded communications.","investigateReports":["Surveillance data supports proceeding to evidence collection. \{suspect_name\}'s premises have been identified. Covert entry plan prepared.","Phase 1 findings support search authorization. \{suspect_name\}'s residence and office have been cased. Entry window identified.","Phase 1 complete. Evidence collection authorized. \{suspect_name\}'s \{premises_type\} ready for covert entry.","Surveillance confirms: \{suspect_name\}'s \{premises_type\} accessible during the identified \{entry_window\}."],"fullBriefs":["EVIDENCE BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 2\\n\\nCovert entry of \{suspect_name\}'s \{premises_type\} is authorized. Entry window: \{entry_window\}.\\n\\nSearch focus: \{search_focus\}. Surveillance team will confirm subject location throughout.\\n\\nRisk assessment: \{entry_risk\}.","EVIDENCE BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 2\\n\\nPremises search of \{suspect_name\}'s \{premises_type\} prepared.\\n\\nSurveillance has identified \{entry_window\} as the optimal window. \{entry_risk\}.\\n\\nSearch priorities: \{search_focus\}. Counter-Intelligence analyst on standby.","EVIDENCE BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 2\\n\\nEntry package ready. \{premises_type\} \'97 \{suspect_name\}. Window: \{entry_window\}.\\n\\nSearch focus: \{search_focus\}. Risk: \{entry_risk\}."],"successOutcomes":["Premises search complete. Evidence recovered: \{evidence_found\}. Subject \{suspect_name\} unaware. Proceeding to apprehension phase.","Covert entry successful. \{evidence_found\} recovered from \{suspect_name\}'s premises. No sign of compromise. Phase 3 authorized.","Search complete. \{evidence_found\} obtained. \{suspect_name\} unaware. Prosecution/neutralization package ready.","\{evidence_found\} recovered cleanly. Entry and exit without detection. Phase 3 authorized."],"failureOutcomes":["Entry compromised. Team extracted without completing search. \{suspect_name\} was notified by an unknown alert system.","Search incomplete. Team discovered a hidden security measure and had to abort. Evidence haul incomplete.","Entry team encountered an unexpected occupant. Extraction without evidence. Cover may be blown.","Technical security system not identified in advance. Team aborted to avoid compromise. Phase 2 inconclusive."],"vars":\{"premises_type":["residence","office","residence and office","storage unit","vehicle and residence","off-site storage"],"entry_window":["a 3-hour gap during subject's daily commute","an overnight window while subject is traveling","a 90-minute lunch break window","a confirmed 4-hour absence on a scheduled appointment"],"entry_risk":["LOW \'97 subject has no known security measures","MODERATE \'97 basic alarm system identified","ELEVATED \'97 subject has shown awareness of surveillance tradecraft","LOW-MODERATE \'97 basic measures, manageable"],"search_focus":["encrypted devices and foreign communications","financial records and payments","operational documents or coded materials","contact lists and meeting records","foreign currency and 