riefs":["APPREHENSION BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 3\\n\\nSubject \{suspect_name\}: arrest authorized on charges of \{charges\}.\\n\\nOptimal apprehension window: \{arrest_window\}. Subject will be isolated from handler contact.\\n\\nPost-arrest: subject to be transferred to \{facility\} for debrief.","APPREHENSION BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 3\\n\\nAll phases complete. Arrest warrant in place for \{charges\}.\\n\\n\{suspect_name\} will be apprehended at \{arrest_window\}. Counter-Intelligence will lead the debrief.","APPREHENSION BRIEF \'97 OP \{codename\} / Phase 3\\n\\nArrest authorization: \{charges\}. Window: \{arrest_window\}.\\n\\n\{suspect_name\} transfer to \{facility\} planned immediately post-arrest."],"successOutcomes":["Subject \{suspect_name\} apprehended. \{charges\} confirmed. Transfer to secure facility underway.","\{suspect_name\} in custody. Clean arrest \'97 no complications, no public exposure. Full debrief initiated.","Arrest executed. \{suspect_name\} at \{facility\}. No resistance, no public exposure. Handler unaware.","\{suspect_name\} apprehended at \{arrest_window\}. Clean operation. Handler not alerted. Debrief commencing."],"failureOutcomes":["Apprehension failed. \{suspect_name\} was tipped off and evaded the arrest team. Subject is now a fugitive.","Arrest attempt compromised. \{suspect_name\} invoked diplomatic protection. Legal challenge filed.","\{suspect_name\} was not at the planned location. Subject appears to have been warned. Now at large.","Arrest team identified before deployment. \{suspect_name\} was notified and departed the country."],"vars":\{"charges":["espionage and unauthorized disclosure of classified material","foreign intelligence activity on domestic soil","conspiracy with a hostile foreign power","providing material support to a hostile intelligence service","theft of classified national security information"],"arrest_window":["during the subject's regular morning commute","at the subject's residence 