hicle. SIGINT passively monitors digital footprint. The goal is to map the subject's daily routine, identify associates, and locate any operational infrastructure \'97 without alerting the subject.","initialReport":"Counter-intelligence review flagged JUNCTION. Assessed as a hostile-linked recruiter. Recommend immediate surveillance.","fullReport":"SURVEILLANCE ASSESSMENT \'97 OP ZIRCON ESTUARY / Phase 1\\n\\nSubject JUNCTION under active surveillance in Washington D.C..\\n\\nmeeting pattern consistent with dead-drop tradecraft. Three unidentified associates have been observed. Digital footprint shows steganographic image uploads to foreign-hosted platforms.\\n\\nRecommend proceeding to Phase 2: Evidence Collection.","successMsgs":["Surveillance phase complete. \{suspect_name\}'s full routine mapped. \{contact_role\} confirmed as regular contact. Proceeding to evidence collection phase.","Phase 1 complete. Surveillance package maintained without compromise. \{digital_anomaly\} flagged for analysis. Phase 2 authorized.","Surveillance successful. Pattern of life established for \{suspect_name\}. Contact activity and digital anomalies documented. Phase 2 ready.","\{suspect_name\} under full surveillance. Routine mapped, associates identified. Proceeding to evidence collection."],"failureMsgs":["Surveillance detected. Subject \{suspect_name\} has gone to ground. Operation will need to be rebuilt from scratch.","Surveillance package blown \'97 a counter-surveillance team spotted our assets. \{suspect_name\} has changed behavior.","\{suspect_name\} performed a surveillance detection route and identified our team. Subject has gone dark.","Technical surveillance compromised. \{suspect_name\} switched devices and changed patterns. Phase 1 inconclusive."],"intelFields":[\{"key":"subject_location","label":"SUBJECT LOCATION","value":"Subject JUNCTION last seen in Washington D.C. \'97 address unconfirmed","revealed":false\},\{"key":"target_profile","label":"TARGET PROFILE","valu