adout. Specialized equipment for covert acquisition and transport prepared and inspected.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1310Z</span> Station FREQUENCY established remote operations link. Assigned role: communications monitoring and early warning.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1540Z</span> Forward staging area established 8km from target location. Communications check completed. All elements confirmed operational.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">26 NOV 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0515Z</span> Final surveillance pass of target location. Target confirmed present. Security detail observed: 5 armed individuals in a rotating patrol.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0830Z</span> SIGINT confirmed target's phone active at location. Voice identification positive. Target is conducting personal calls \'97 appears relaxed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1015Z</span> Approach route finalized. Primary: helicopter insertion to a nearby clearing. Alternate route briefed in case of compromise.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1350Z</span> Weather forecast for execution window: Scattered cloud cover, moonlit. Assessment: FAVORABLE.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">29 NOV 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0100Z</span> H-HOUR MINUS 60. Final intelligence update: target confirmed at location. No unusual activity detected. GO authorization confirmed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0122Z</span> CONDOR assault element departed staging area. Scattered cloud cover, moonlit. All teams moving to assigned positions.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0200Z</span> SIGINT jammed hostile communications on the field commander's order during the final phase.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0203Z</span> HUMINT sour