ures in effect.","SIGINT support lost due to local jamming. CURARE moved from known location. Surveillance picture partially degraded."],"confSuccess":[3,7],"confFail":[-6,-12],"intelFields":[\{"key":"target_pattern","label":"MOVEMENT PATTERN","value":"Pattern partially mapped \'97 predictable daily route with consistent timing, gaps remain","revealed":true\},\{"key":"contact_network","label":"CONTACT NETWORK","value":"a person with known connections to a hostile state embassy \'97 confirmed contact, meeting pattern established","revealed":true\},\{"key":"residence","label":"RESIDENCE","value":"Probable residence: a commercial premises used as a cover address \'97 not yet confirmed","revealed":true\},\{"key":"comm_device","label":"COMMUNICATIONS","value":"Communication method likely a diplomatic communication channel \'97 not fully confirmed","revealed":true\},\{"key":"movement_window","label":"ACTION WINDOW","value":"a recurring evening meeting at an isolated location \'97 optimal window confirmed","revealed":true\}],"intelBonus":true,"blown":false,"blownDaysLeft":0,"lastInvOutcome":"CRITICAL_SUCCESS","agencyJustification":"The target is a high-value individual operating in a permissive but sensitive foreign environment. Direct action without surveillance preparation risks exposure and mission failure. A covert surveillance package will establish the pattern of life and operational window required to authorize a rendition or neutralization operation.","linkedHvtId":"H51","attachedEliteIds":[],"agencySupport":[],"debriefHtml":"<div class=\\"db-wrap db-success\\"><div class=\\"db-toggle\\" onclick=\\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('db-open')\\"><span class=\\"db-toggle-arrow\\">&#9654;</span><span class=\\"db-toggle-label\\">FULL OPERATIONAL DEBRIEF</span></div><div class=\\"db-body\\"><div class=\\"db-classification\\">TOP SECRET // SCI</div><div class=\\"db-title\\">AFTER-ACTION REPORT</div><div class=\\"db-subtitle\\">OP OPAL SQUALL \'97 OBJECTIVES ACHIEVED</