gy \'97 full intercept not yet established. Counter-surv posture: advanced \'97 regular SDR, difficult to follow without compromise. Abduction window confirmed."],"failureMsgs":["Surveillance detected. KINGPIN performed a counter-surveillance sweep and identified our team. Target has changed routines and may relocate.","Surveillance package blown. Target KINGPIN was alerted by an unknown source. Residence and movement data incomplete.","KINGPIN unexpectedly departed Seattle before the surveillance package could be fully established. Target location unknown.","Technical surveillance compromised. KINGPIN switched communication devices and changed patterns. Operational picture incomplete.","Field team burned. KINGPIN identified the surveillance asset during a routine counter-surveillance route. Target now elevated security posture.","Surveillance aborted when local security forces became aware of unusual activity. KINGPIN has gone to ground."],"confSuccess":[3,7],"confFail":[-5,-10],"intelFields":[\{"key":"target_pattern","label":"MOVEMENT PATTERN","value":"weekly meetings at three rotating locations \'97 confirmed by three separate observation sessions","revealed":true\},\{"key":"contact_network","label":"CONTACT NETWORK","value":"a domestic national under a separate investigation \'97 confirmed contact, meeting frequency established","revealed":true\},\{"key":"residence","label":"RESIDENCE","value":"a hotel in the city centre \'97 residence confirmed by field team","revealed":true\},\{"key":"comm_device","label":"COMMUNICATIONS","value":"Communication method observed: face-to-face dead-drop methodology \'97 full intercept not yet established","revealed":true\},\{"key":"movement_window","label":"ACTION WINDOW","value":"Possible window: a weekly 4-hour window when target travels alone \'97 not yet fully confirmed","revealed":true\}],"intelBonus":false,"blown":false,"blownDaysLeft":0,"lastInvOutcome":"SUCCESS","agencyJustification":"The target is a known threat actor op