deo evidence.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1055Z</span> Associate identified: a previously unknown contact \'97 now flagged for investigation.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">13 NOV 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0600Z</span> Final collection day. All remaining intelligence gaps addressed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0820Z</span> Surveillance package withdrawn. All teams extracted sequentially to avoid pattern recognition.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1010Z</span> Final intelligence package compiled: 16 pages of analysis, 58 photographs, 29 communications intercepts, and complete pattern-of-life documentation.</div><div class=\\"db-section-title\\">ASSESSMENT</div><div class=\\"db-assessment\\">Extended surveillance of KINGPIN in Seattle has been completed. FIELD OPS field team, COUNTER-INTEL officer, ANALYSIS desk, HUMINT handler, SIGINT intercept team maintained covert observation for 3 days without detection. Section BULWARK identified critical patterns and contacts that were not previously known. Key products: complete pattern of life, 5 safe house locations, 3 associate identities, communications patterns mapped, and security detail assessment (1 personnel). This intelligence package enables high-confidence direct-action planning against the target.</div></div></div>","archivedDay":312\},\{"id":"M113","typeId":"HVT_ABDUCTION_FOR","codename":"ROUGE TIDE","threat":5,"label":"FOREIGN RENDITION","category":"RENDITION OPS","location":"FOREIGN","city":"Bamako","country":"Mali","urgency":15,"urgencyLeft":3,"fillVars":\{"city":"Bamako","country":"Mali","codename":"ROUGE TIDE","urgency_days":"15","agency":"SAA","leaderTitle":"the President","bureau_name":"BUREAU","agency_name":"AGENCY","military_name":"DIA","alias":"RAPTOR","hvt_role":"propaganda coordinator","snatch_window":"a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed 