posure: zero.","initialReport":"Pattern-of-life data on RAPTOR in Mali is complete. Snatch window: a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance. Foreign rendition authorized.","fullReport":"RENDITION BRIEF \'97 OP ROUGE TIDE\\n\\nTarget: RAPTOR. Mali operation.\\n\\na daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance \'97 window confirmed. Location: a hotel under a false booking. Security: light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance.\\n\\nExtraction: Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed. Transport: Transport: a charter aircraft pre-positioned at a secondary airfield \'97 pre-positioning confirmation pending.","successMsgs":["Foreign rendition complete. RAPTOR captured at a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance in Bamako. Security light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance managed without escalation. Extraction via Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed succeeded. Target in secure transit.","RAPTOR successfully renditioned from Mali. Snatch window used as planned. Extraction route Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed clean. Transport Transport: a charter aircraft pre-positioned at a secondary airfield \'97 pre-positioning confirmation pending delivered target to secure facility.","Capture operation complete. RAPTOR (propaganda coordinator) taken at a hotel under a false booking. Security: light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance managed. Extraction: Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed. No attribution. Target in transit.","Rendition successful. RAPTOR taken from Bamako. Window: a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance. Security managed. Extraction Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed via Transport: a charter aircraft pre-positioned at a secondary airfield \'97 pre-positioning confirmation pending. Zero attribution. Mali authorities unaware.","Foreign rendition complete. Target RAPTOR secured. Extraction from Mali successful via Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed. No witnesses, no trace, no attribution.","RAPTOR renditioned from a hotel under a false booking in Bamako. Security: light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance \'97 managed. Route: Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed. Transport: Transport: a charter aircraft pre-positioned at a secondary airfield \'97 pre-positioning confirmation pending. Clean operation with full deniability."],"failureMsgs":["Rendition team compromised before execution. RAPTOR was warned and departed a hotel under a false booking hours before the operation. Mali security forces may be aware.","Snatch attempt in Bamako failed. Security detail light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance was larger than assessed. Team extracted under contact. RAPTOR is now aware of the threat.","RAPTOR was not at the planned location during the a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance. Target may have altered schedule. Foreign operation aborted.","Extraction route Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed was compromised. Team aborted capture. RAPTOR alerted and has increased security posture.","Snatch operation blown. Local security services were alerted before team could execute. RAPTOR now under protective security. International exposure risk elevated.","Team was identified on approach. Abort ordered. RAPTOR escaped. Mali authorities responding. Diplomatic exposure possible."],"confSuccess":[8,14],"confFail":[-12,-20],"intelFields":[\{"key":"snatch_window","label":"SNATCH WINDOW","value":"a daily exercise route with minimal security coverage \'97 confirmed by surveillance","revealed":true\},\{"key":"entry_route","label":"ENTRY ROUTE","value":"Entry plan confirmed and pre-staged","revealed":true\},\{"key":"security_detail","label":"SECURITY DETAIL","value":"light (3-man security detail) \'97 fully characterized by surveillance","revealed":true\},\{"key":"extraction_route","label":"EXTRACTION ROUTE","value":"Route planned: overland through allied territory to a friendly border crossing \'97 viability unconfirmed","revealed":true\},\{"key":"transport_asset","label":"TRANSPORT ASSET","value":"Transport: a charter aircraft pre-positioned at a secondary airfield \'97 pre-positioning confirmation pending","revealed":true\}],"intelBonus":false,"blown":false,"blownDaysLeft":0,"lastInvOutcome":"SUCCESS","agencyJustification":"The target is operating in a country with no extradition arrangement and a hostile intelligence environment. Legal prosecution is not feasible. The target holds critical intelligence value that cannot be obtained through any other means. Rendition authority has been personally authorized by the President. SAA covert operations teams are the only instrument capable of executing this action with full deniability.","linkedHvtId":"H40","isAbduction":true,"attachedEliteIds":["EU2","EU10"],"agencySupport":[],"debriefHtml":"<div class=\\"db-wrap db-success\\"><div class=\\"db-toggle\\" onclick=\\"this.parentElement.classList.toggle('db-open')\\"><span class=\\"db-toggle-arrow\\">&#9654;</span><span class=\\"db-toggle-label\\">FULL OPERATIONAL DEBRIEF</span></div><div class=\\"db-body\\"><div class=\\"db-classification\\">TOP SECRET // ORCON</div><div class=\\"db-title\\">AFTER-ACTION REPORT</div