b-time\\">1635Z</span> Element RAPTOR briefed on primary role: overwatch and sniper support.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1710Z</span> Forward staging area established 9km from target location. Communications check completed. All elements confirmed operational.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">28 OCT 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0820Z</span> Final surveillance pass of target location. Target confirmed present. Security detail observed: 1 armed individuals in a mobile escort configuration.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1025Z</span> SIGINT confirmed target's phone active at location. Voice identification positive. Target is conducting personal calls \'97 appears relaxed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1315Z</span> Approach route finalized. Primary: foot infiltration through adjacent property. Alternate route briefed in case of compromise.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1510Z</span> Weather forecast for execution window: Overcast, ceiling at 800ft. Assessment: FAVORABLE.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">30 OCT 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0200Z</span> H-HOUR MINUS 60. Final intelligence update: target confirmed at location. No unusual activity detected. GO authorization confirmed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0220Z</span> REAPER assault element departed staging area. Overcast, ceiling at 800ft. All teams moving to assigned positions.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0259Z</span> HUMINT handler maintained contact with a local asset providing real-time ground truth from inside the target area.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0305Z</span> SIGINT intercept team monitored all target communications throughout the operation.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0317Z</span> Outer security perimeter established. 3 escape routes blocked by SPECIAL OPS elements.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0329Z</span> H-HOUR. Element RAPTOR led breach element. Entry via stealth infiltration through rear access. Security detail neutralized within seconds.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0337Z</span> Target located in the basement. Subjects appeared shocked by the speed of entry. Compliance was immediate.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0343Z</span> Target positively identified via document verification. Identity confirmed: RAPTOR.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0347Z</span> Target sedated per medical protocol and transferred to prepared transport vehicle. Cover story for disappearance will be no cover \'97 clean disappearance.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0357Z</span> Site exploitation team entered. 25 minutes of rapid evidence collection. Items recovered: communications equipment including encrypted radios.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0401Z</span> Extraction commenced via commercial cover \'97 targets moved via civilian transport under guard. All teams departed area of operations. No pursuit detected. REAPER confirmed clean extraction.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0420Z</span> Target delivered to forward operating base for initial interrogation. Chain of custody documented. All FOREIGN OPS/SPECIAL OPS/HUMINT/SIGINT elements accounted for and RTB.</div><div class=\\"db-section-title\\">ASSESSMENT</div><div class=\\"db-assessment\\">High-value target RAPTOR has been successfully acquired in Bamako. The operation was executed by FOREIGN OPS cell, SPECIAL OPS strike unit, HUMINT handler, SIGINT intercept team with elite asset Element RAPTOR attached. Total operation time from breach to extraction: approximately 64 minutes. The target is now in secure custody and has indicated willingness to cooperate on certain topics. Seized materials from the target location are undergoing exploitation by the Analysis Bureau. Early assessment suggests significant intelligence value. Operational security was maintained. No attribution to SAA is expected. FOREIGN OPS/SPECIAL OPS/HUMINT/SIGINT performance rated OUTSTANDING.</div></div></div>","archivedDay":298\},\{"id":"M112","typeId":"DOMESTIC_TERROR","codename":"JADE BASTION","threat":4,"label":"DOMESTIC THREAT","category":"COUNTER-TERRORISM","location":"DOMESTIC","city":"Seattle","country":"United States","urgency":10,"urgencyLeft":1,"fillVars":\{"city":"Seattle","country":"United States","codename":"JADE BASTION","urgency_days":"10","agency":"SAA","leaderTitle":"the President","bureau_name":"BUREAU","agency_name":"AGENCY","military_name":"DIA","group":"radicalized nationals","attack_type":"a power grid disruption","target":"a crowded market","alias":"VIPER","cell_size":"2","casualties":"21","reliability":"SINGLE-SOURCE","cell_location":"Confirmed: Seattle a crowded market area \'97 building identified","cell_leader":"Alias \\"VIPER\\" \'97 identity unverified, single-source","attack_vector":"a power grid disruption \'97 method suspected, materials pattern consistent","attack_timeline":"10-day window \'97 attack assessed as imminent","arms_status":"Weapons acquisition complete \'97 ready to deploy"\},"isMultiPhase":false,"status":"ARCHIVED","assignedInvDept":null,"invDaysLeft":0,"assignedBudget":3,"assignedExecDepts":["FIELD_OPS","SPECIAL_OPS","HUMINT","SIGINT"],"execDaysLeft":0,"successProb":92,"resultMsg":"Operation successful. \\"VIPER\\" and 2 operatives apprehended. a power grid disruption threat eliminated.\\n\\nFull debriefing of the cell leader is underway. Early indications suggest the cell had foreign logistical support.","confDelta":16,"budgetDelta":0,"dayReceived":280,"phaseFalseFlag":false,"phaseFalseFlagText":"","phaseFalseFlagPenalty":false,"followUpSpawned":false,"suspects":[\{"alias":"FALCON","role":"low-value contact","confidence":"MODERATE","isTarget":false,"eliminated":true\},\{"alias":"WOLF","role":"suspected cell leader","confidence":"LOW","isTarget":true,"eliminated":false\}],"selectedSuspectIdx":1,"invDays":4,"execDays":3,"baseBudget":6,"invDepts":["ANALYSIS","HUMINT","SIGINT","FIELD_OPS"],"execDepts":["FIELD_OPS","SPECIAL_OPS"],"opNarrative":"Field teams establish a tactical perimeter and move to neutralize the cell. HUMINT assets provide real-time target guidance while SIGINT intercepts communications. Special Operations holds in reserve for direct-action if the cell is armed. A simultaneous multi-point breach minimizes the risk of suspects fleeing.","initialReport":"Credible threat report: radicalized nationals planning action against a crowded market. Timeline unknown. Source reliability: SINGLE-SOURCE.","fullReport":"INTELLIGENCE BRIEF \'97 OP JADE BASTION\\n\\nCell composition: 2 individuals confirmed. Additional members possible. Cell leader operating under alias \\"VIPER\\".\\n\\nObjective: a power grid disruption targeting a crowded market in Seattle.\\n\\nTimeline: window of 10 days remaining.\\n\\nAssessment: Threat credible. Immediate action recommended.","successMsgs":["Cell neutralized. \{cell_size\} suspects detained. Materials seized. Planned attack against \{target\} prevented. No civilian casualties.\\n\\nPost-operation assessment confirms the cell was days from executing. HUMINT source proved reliable throughout.","Operation successful. \\"\{alias\}\\" and \{cell_size\} operatives apprehended. \{attack_type\} threat eliminated.\\n\\nFull debriefing of the cell leader is underway. Early indications suggest the cell had foreign logistical support.","Cell dismantled. Attack on \{target\} prevented. \{cell_size\} suspects in custody, materials secured.\\n\\nForensic teams are exploiting seized devices. Preliminary review suggests links to other domestic networks.","Operation complete. \\"\{alias\}\\" captured. \{cell_size\} associates detained. \{attack_type\} capability seized and destroyed.\\n\\nThe attack had been weeks in planning. Disruption at this stage prevents significant casualties."],"failureMsgs":["Operation blown. Cell received advance warning and dispersed. \{attack_type\} against \{target\} proceeded \'97 \{casualties\} casualties reported.\\n\\nThe source of the operational leak is under investigation. The cell leader \\"\{alias\}\\" remains at large.","Insufficient intelligence led to premature deployment. Field teams arrived post-event. \{casualties\} casualties. Cell leader \\"\{alias\}\\" remains at large.","Raid failed to locate cell. \\"\{alias\}\\" had already relocated. \{attack_type\} threat remains active.\\n\\n\{casualties\} casualties confirmed. Security review of the intelligence chain initiated.","Deployment compromised. Cell was warned. \\"\{alias\}\\" and associates scattered across the region.\\n\\nThe attack on \{target\} may still be active. Counter-terrorism units placed on heightened readiness."],"confSuccess":[10,18],"confFail":[-18,-30],"intelFields":[\{"key":"cell_location","label":"CELL LOCATION","value":"Confirmed: Seattle a crowded market area \'97 building identified","revealed":true\},\{"key":"cell_leader","label":"CELL LEADER IDENTITY","value":"Alias \\"VIPER\\" \'97 identity unverified, single-source","revealed":true\},\{"key":"attack_vector","label":"ATTACK METHOD","value":"a power grid disruption \'97 method suspected, materials pattern consistent","revealed":true\},\{"key":"attack_timeline","label":"OPERATIONAL TIMELINE","value":"10-day window \'97 attack assessed as imminent","revealed":true\},\{"key":"arms_status","label":"WEAPONS STATUS","value":"Weapons acquisition complete \'97 ready to deploy","revealed":true\}],"intelBonus":true,"blown":false,"blownDaysLeft":0,"lastInvOutcome":"SUCCESS","agencyJustification":"The source intelligence is derived from a classified SIGINT program unavailable to law enforcement counte