"db-time\\">0915Z</span> DELTA team assembled at forward staging area. Operational briefing conducted by FIELD OPS/SPECIAL OPS/HUMINT/SIGINT command element. Weather assessment: Pre-dawn darkness, new moon.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1130Z</span> Advance reconnaissance team deployed to Seattle. Confirmed target building visual. Building is a row house in residential neighborhood.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1305Z</span> SIGINT intercept team established electronic surveillance perimeter. All target communications monitored in real-time. 6 active devices detected within the target structure.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1615Z</span> Surveillance team (CONDOR) reported 2 individuals observed entering the building over a 2-hour period. Pattern consistent with cell meeting.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">1830Z</span> SPECIAL OPS element confirmed no counter-surveillance activity detected around the target area. Approach routes validated.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-day\\">22 OCT 2025</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0130Z</span> Final intelligence update received. All 2 subjects confirmed present at target location. GO authorization received from Director.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0201Z</span> DELTA assault element departed staging area. 5 vehicles in convoy. Radio silence enforced. ETA to target: 12 minutes.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0231Z</span> HUMINT source confirmed target disposition 57 minutes before H-hour, enabling final GO decision.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0240Z</span> SIGINT provided real-time electronic surveillance \'97 scanning radio frequencies and phone networks in the target area.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0251Z</span> Outer cordon established by FIELD OPS team. 4 positions covering all egress points. Local law enforcement discreetly diverted from the area of operations.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0303Z</span> Element RAPTOR led the primary assault element to breach point. Final equipment check completed. Weapons status confirmed.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0310Z</span> H-HOUR. Breach initiated via stealth infiltration through rear access. Subjects appeared shocked by the speed of entry. Compliance was immediate. Entry to target achieved in under 18 seconds.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0314Z</span> Ground floor cleared. 1 subjects detained in the main room. Element RAPTOR personally secured \\"VIPER\\" who was found hiding in a back room.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0322Z</span> Building fully cleared room by room. Total subjects detained: 2. One assault team member sustained a minor bruise during entry \'97 no medical treatment required.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0326Z</span> Sensitive site exploitation team entered the building. Evidence recovery initiated. Items catalogued on-site include: hard drives containing operational planning documents. Additionally recovered: surveillance photography of 4 potential targets.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0335Z</span> All 2 detainees processed, photographed, and biometrically registered. \\"VIPER\\" positively identified via facial recognition database match. Transport to secure holding facility arranged.</div>\\n<div class=\\"db-event\\"><span class=\\"db-time\\">0349Z</span> Area of operations fully sanitized. No forensic evidence of agency involvement left on-site. DELTA team and all support elements returned to base. Operation concluded.</div><div class=\\"db-section-title\\">ASSESSMENT</div><div class=\\"db-assessment\\">The operation against the radicalized nationals cell in Seattle achieved all objectives. The planned a power grid disruption against a crowded market has been permanently disrupted. 2 operatives are in custody, including cell leader \\"VIPER\\". Intelligence exploitation of seized materials is the immediate priority \'97 hard drives containing operational planning documents are expected to yield significant insights into the wider network. Element RAPTOR performance during the breach phase was exemplary and directly contributed to the rapid, non-lethal subduing of the primary target. Operational security was maintained throughout. No media or public awareness of the operation has been detected. FIELD OPS/SPECIAL OPS/HUMINT/SIGINT coordination rated EXCELLENT. Recommend commendation for DELTA team leader.</div></div></div>","archivedDay":291\},\{"id":"M111","typeId":"HVT_ABDUCTION_DOM","codename":"CRIMSON STORM","threat":3,"label":"HVT ABDUCTION","category":"RENDITION OPS","location":"DOMESTIC","city":"Seattle","country":"United States","urgency":14,"urgencyLeft":5,"fillVars":\{"city":"Seattle","country":"United States","codename":"CRIMSON STORM","urgency_days":"14","agency":"SAA","leaderTitle":"the President","bureau_name":"BUREAU","agency_name":"AGENCY","military_name":"DIA","alias":"HAMMER","hvt_role":"cell coordinator","snatch_window":"Possible window: a regular unaccompanied appointment \'97 timing not yet fully confirmed","security_detail":"Security posture estimated: none \'97 target operating alone \'97 confirmation pending","extraction_route":"Extraction route planned: overland through pre-cleared checkpoints \'97 viability unconfirmed","transport_asset":"a pre-positioned ambulance cover vehicle \'97 confirmed and pre-positioned","location_detail":"a residential address under surveillance","entry_route":"Entry route confirmed \'97 access plan finalized","target_alias":"HAMMER","suspect_name":"HAMMER","target_role":"cell coordinator","rendition_role":"cell coordinator"\},"isMultiPhase":false,"status":"ARCHIVED","assignedInvDept":nu